title: A Tasmanian Time Capsule
abstract: A glimpse into the past, a fascinating series of films about Tasmania from the National Film and Sound Archive.
description: A collection of films about Tasmania sourced from the NFSA's collection. The Australian island of Tasmania has long been promoted for its unusual and unique flora and fauna and its natural unspoilt beauty. These early films represent a record of events, a range of traditional industries including agriculture and farming, and Tasmanians at their leisurely best!
